%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Getting%20a%20job%20is%20hard.%20A%20trade%20war%20is%20only%20going%20to%20make%20it%20harder.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225900%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Trump%20holds%20up%20a%20graph%20that%20supposedly%20shows%20how%20much%20tariff%20other%20countries%20have%20on%20the%20US%2C%20versus%20what%20he%20calls%20%26quot%3Breciprocal%20tariffs.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67edcb57b8b41a9673fc7e75%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223933%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20is%20enacting%20tariffs%20that%20economists%20say%20could%20slow%20hiring%20as%20businesses%20face%20uncertainty.%3Cp%3ECarlos%20Barria%2FREUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20widening%20tariff%20fight%20could%20slow%20hiring%20across%20a%20range%20of%20industries.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famericans-worried-tariffs-stock-up-essentials-cut-back-luxuries-2025-4%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIncreased%20trade%20barriers%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20also%20hurt%20hiring%20in%20areas%20that%20have%20been%20strong%2C%20like%20retail.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhite-collar%20hiring%2C%20which%20has%20been%20weak%2C%20might%20not%20get%20hit%20as%20much%2C%20one%20economist%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20expanding%20tariff%20fight%20could%20push%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-workers-tough-job-search-private-sector-roles-layoffs-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20job%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20meh%20to%20miserable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichelle%20Budnick%2C%20a%20documentary%20filmmaker%20in%20New%20York%2C%20worries%20that%20her%20search%20will%20get%20harder.%20The%2047-year-old%20has%20been%20looking%20for%20full-time%20production%20work%20for%20over%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBudnick%20told%