ruary%202022%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20a%20lovely%20life%20there%2C%20especially%20in%20terms%20of%20safety%2C%20efficiency%2C%20and%20cleanliness%2C%20but%20we%20still%20hadn't%20moved%20on%20from%20our%20US-based%20corporate%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20worked%20around%20the%20clock%2C%20barely%20spending%20much%20downtime%20together%20because%20it%20was%20all%20about%20making%20money%20to%20afford%20to%20live%20the%20Singapore%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20condo%20was%20nice%2C%20but%20we%20have%20a%20Rottweiler%20named%20Raja%2C%20and%20sharing%20common%20walls%20was%20also%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2212d7a4fb-0cc7-4587-9f0a-03843b1ed9b6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%20of%20the%20first%20holidays%20we%20took%20from%20Singapore%20was%20to%20Koh%20Samui%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20immediately%20fell%20in%20love%20and%20began%20speaking%20with%20real%20estate%20agents%20because%20we%20wanted%20to%20buy%20a%20vacation%20home%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20we%20started%20thinking%20about%20quality%20of%20life%20and%20our%20end%20goal.%20Did%20we%20want%20to%20keep%20climbing%20the%20corporate%20ladder%2C%20or%20focus%20on%20our%20happiness%20and%20creative%20freedom%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223223c571-abc0-455a-a7a2-af6ea5b63eb8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThese%20considerations%20led%20to%20us%20quitting%20our%20jobs%20and%20moving%20to%20Koh%20Samui%20full-time%20in%20July%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20live%20where%20some%20of%20the%20most%20recent%20season%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-white-lotus-real-filming-locations-season-three-thailand-phuket-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20White%20Lotus%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20was%20filmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20love%20the%20show%20and%20were%20thrilled%20to%20hear%20that%20season%20three%20was%20being%20filmed%20in%20Koh%20Samui.%20Several%20of%20our%20friends%20were%20on%20set%20as%20extras.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20can't%20wait%20for%20the%20finale.%20It's%20been%20exciting%20to%20recognize%20familiar%20places%20on%20the%20island%20featured%20on%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a86b881b-01b7-4e8a-9804-249726f245bb%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20have%20a%20visa%20issued%20through%20the%20Thailand%20Bureau%20of%20Investment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20visa%20is%20called%20a%20'%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmart-visa.boi.go.th%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESmart%20Visa%3C%2Fa%3E.'%20Our%20program%20is%20designed%20to%20attract%20startup%20entrepreneurs%20investing%20in%20targeted%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoving%20our%20dog%20was%20the%20most%20important%20thing.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe'd%20had%20support%20with%20our%20relocations%20to%20Shanghai%20and%20Singapore%2C%20but%20we%20had%20to%20do%20it%20ourselves%20for%20Thailand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223935%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20rottweiler%20on%20a%20beach%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f0383563d72727e19946a6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222952%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERaja%20at%20the%20beach.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Justin%20and%20Kelly%20Harris%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20we%20decided%20to%20move%20here%2C%20we%20haven't%20looked%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226a8cca38-8e53-4b3d-bd6b-16c533d9ec95%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENavigating%20real%20estate%20was%20the%20most%20difficult%20part%20of%20the%20move%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222705%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20pool%20and%20house%20in%20Thailand%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f0387863d72727e19946bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221522%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EView%20of%20the%20house%20from%20Justin%20and%20Kelly's%20pool.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Justin%20and%20Kelly%20Harris%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHouse%20hunting%20in%20Koh%20Samui%20is%20very%20different%20from%20LA.%20There's%20no%20centralized%20database%3B%20less%20than%2050%25%20of%20properties%20are%20listed%20online.%20Many%20homes%20are%20sold%20through%20word%20of%20mouth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERenovations%20were%20difficult%2C%20too.%20Coming%20from%20an%20urban%20environment%20with%20much%20more%20routine%2C%20structure%2C%20and%20predictability%2C%20getting%20used%20to%20doing%20something%20on%20an%20island%20can%20be%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20experience%20made%20us%20much%20more%20adaptable%20and%20flexible.%20Whereas%20things%20in%20the%20past%20may%20have%20been%20frustrating%2C%20now%20we%20can%20laugh%20it%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22556e79b0-61b2-42a6-9295-9ee0ed715b42%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20started%20taking%20Thai%20lessons%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20this%20year%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20took%20Mandarin%20lessons%20when%20we%20lived%20in%20China%20and%20thought%20they%20might%20help%2C%20but%20they've%20made%20it%20more%20confusing%2C%20as%20some%20words%20are%20similar%20but%20have%20completely%20different%20meanings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20want%20to%20be%20conversational%20in%20Thai%2C%20but%20English%20is%20fairly%20widespread%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2224452f9f-daed-415d-bb1d-b2ea456ab9af%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20started%20our%20own%20architecture%2C%20branding%2C%20and%20concept%20design%20studio%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20run%20a%20studio%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.snobbirds.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESnobBirds%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20work%20remotely%2C%20with%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emost%20projects%20based%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Singapore%2C%20and%20Hong%20Kong.%20We%20have%20a%20truly%20flexible%20schedule%20and%20are%20available%20for%20clients%20whenever%20they%20need%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20work%20is%20entirely%20project-based%2C%20so%20our%20hours%20fluctuate.%20Some%20weeks%20are%20intense%20(60%2B%20hours)%2C%20while%20others%20are%20lighter%20(20%20hours).%20We%20regularly%20worked%2070-80%20hours%20a%20week%20in%20our%20corporate%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20difference%20now%20is%20control%20%E2%80%94%20we%20choose%20projects%20we're%20passionate%20about%20and%20pass%20on%20those%20that%20aren't%20a%20good%20fit.%20When%20work%20slows%20down%2C%20we%20can%20fully%20embrace%20island%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2290cd31e5-a495-49d8-9e63-4417e8d34766%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20love%20to%20use%20our%20personal%20time%20to%20experience%20the%20island%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20road%20trips%20and%20take%20the%20ferry%20to%20the%20mainland%20to%20drive%20into%20Thailand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKoh%20Samui%20is%20quite%20diverse.%20The%20exposure%20to%20the%20international%20community%20is%20part%20of%20what%20drove%20us%20to%20come%20to%20this%20island%20because%20you%20get%20a%20taste%20of%20both%20worlds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20came%20here%20because%20we%20wanted%20to%20experience%20a%20new%20culture%20and%20foods%20and%20learn%20a%20new%20language.%20We%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20comfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226650c689-cb84-4d8b-a514-03b9190792bd%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%20of%20the%20best%20things%20about%20living%20here%20is%20the%20Thai%20food%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20get%20great%20Thai%20food%20for%20under%20%2410%3B%20great%20seafood%20along%20the%20coast%20is%20a%20little%20more%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20food%20quality%20is%20excellent.%20However%2C%20cheese%20and%20imported%20beer%2C%20wine%2C%20and%20spirits%20are%2050%25%20to%2075%25%20more%20expensive.%20There's%20also%20variety%2C%20as%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20international%20food%20on%20the%20island%2C%20especially%20from%20the%20expat%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20community%20is%20very%20tight-knit.%20We%20don't%20know%20many%20places%20where%20you'll%20shop%20at%20the%20same%20grocery%20store%20in%20the%20morning%20with%20a%20local%20restaurant%20owner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22923a121b-66a0-4dc7-a88b-6afcf7fe8810%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20cost%20of%20living%20in%20Koh%20Samui%20is%20another%20advantage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20bought%20our%20house%20in%20LA%2C%20now%20a%20rental%2C%20for%20just%20over%20%241M%20in%202017%20by%20taking%20out%20a%20loan%20and%2030-year%20mortgage.%20The%20house%20in%20Koh%20Samui%20was%20one-third%20the%20cost%2C%20and%20we%20purchased%20it%20outright%20with%20cash%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20cost%20of%20living%20in%20Koh%20Samui%20is%20significantly%20lower%20since%20our%20house%20is%20paid%20off%2C%20and%20we%20share%20a%20car%20without%20a%20car%20payment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2218d5a9d2-6de6-4515-9754-2e7e184c312e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20miss%20our%20family%20and%20friends%20the%20most%20and%20try%20to%20go%20back%20home%20to%20LA%20once%20a%20year%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223903%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20sunset%20overlooking%20the%20water%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f038b463d72727e19946ca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222927%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20view%20from%20the%20roof%20terrace%20at%20Justin%20and%20Kelly's%20house.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Justin%20and%20Kelly%20Harris%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20we%20still%20have%20our%20house%20in%20California%2C%20if%20we%20need%20to%20split%20our%20time%20more%20for%20our%20business%20or%20family%2C%20we%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20families%20have%20been%20great%20about%20visiting%20us%20and%20love%20having%20the%20excuse%20to%20experience%20more%20of%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20imagine%20we'll%20return%20home%20at%20some%20point%2C%20but%20there's%20no%20end%20date%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-