20until%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20MG%20badge%20never%20disappeared%20from%20British%20showrooms%20and%20the%20Chinese-made%20cars%20have%20become%20increasingly%20popular%20there.%20The%20brand%20notched%20up%20record%20sales%20of%20just%20over%2081%2C000%20vehicles%20last%20year%2C%20putting%20MG%20in%2010th%20place%20for%20registrations%2C%20with%20a%20market%20share%20of%20almost%204.2%25.%20About%20one%20in%20four%20MGs%20sold%20were%20electric.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20MG4%20hatchback%20was%20the%20fourth%20best-selling%20EV%20in%20the%20UK%20last%20year%20and%20was%20the%20second%20most%20popular%20model%20with%20private%20(as%20opposed%20to%20fleet)%20buyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20appeal%20is%20probably%20down%20to%20the%20prices%2C%20which%20range%20from%20%C2%A327%2C000%20(just%20under%20%2435%2C000)%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0about%20%C2%A313%2C000%20less%20than%20the%20cheapest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20about%20the%20same%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbyd-xpeng-china-ev-crushing-tesla-going-global-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBYD%3C%2Fa%3E%20Dolphin%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0through%20to%20%C2%A336%2C500%20(about%20%2447%2C000.)%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20what's%20the%20MG4%20like%20to%20drive%3F%20I%20had%20the%20most%20expensive%20XPower%20version%2C%20which%20promises%200%20to%2062%20miles%20an%20hour%20in%203.8%20seconds%20from%20the%2064kWh%20battery%20%E2%80%94%20half%20the%20time%20the%20long-range%20model%20takes.%20(A%20test%20by%20What%20Car%3F%20got%20the%20Xpower%20to%2060mph%20in%20just%203.6%20seconds%20%E2%80%94%20faster%2C%20they%20say%2C%20than%20a%20Porsche%20Taycan%204S.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20boasts%20all-wheel%20drive%2C%20enhanced%20brakes%2C%20launch%20control%20%2Cand%20has%20a%20claimed%20maximum%20driving%20range%20of%20between%20239%20miles%20on%20the%20WLTP%20measure%2C%20and%20328%20miles%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22MG4%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67deb8a169253ccddf9a0d1c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20orange%20calipers%20are%20a%20nice%20visual%20touch%20on%20the%20MG4%20XPower.%3Cp%3EBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20rather%20liked%20the%20shade%20of%20matte%20green%2C%20although%20the%20styling%20may%20not%20win%20any%20design%20awards.%20As%20far%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgodfather-of-evs-explains-why-china-is-winning-ev-race-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChinese%20EVs%3C%2Fa%3E%20go%2C%20it%20could%20be%20much%20worse.%20The%20flashy%20alloy%20wheels%20with%20orange%20brake%20calipers%20are%20a%20nice%20touch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInside%2C%20the%20seven-inch%20screen%20behind%20the%20(leather-clad)%20steering%20wheel%20is%20complemented%20by%20a%20larger%2C%20wider%20central%20screen%20with%20entertainment%20and%20navigation%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20pleased%20to%20find%20a%20row%20of%20good%2C%20old-fashioned%20physical%20buttons%20for%20volume%2C%20fan%2C%20and%20hazard%20lights.%20However%2C%20connecting%20my%20iPhone%20to%20the%20sound%20system%20was%20a%20fiddlier%20experience%20than%20it%20needed%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22MG4%20XPower%20dashboard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67deb90269253ccddf9a0d1e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20screens%20are%20a%20sensible%20size%20%E2%80%94%20and%20there%20are%20some%20physical%20buttons%20too.%3Cp%3EBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20the%20MG4%20south%20of%20London%20one%20gloomy%20Sunday%20to%20a%20scenic%20spot%20called%20Box%20Hill.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbyd-seal-electric-car-review-test-drive-elon-musk-tesla-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnlike%20other%20cars%20I've%20driven%20for%20BI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20did%20not%20scold%20me%20the%20moment%20I%20exceeded%20the%20speed%20limit%20by%20even%201%20mile%20an%20hour%20%E2%80%94%20a%20blessed%20relief%20given%20many%20roads%20have%20a%2020%20mph%20limit.%20More%20bonus%20brownie%20points.%20It's%20a%20breeze%20to%20drive%2C%20and%20as%20I%20suggested%20above%20it%20goes%20like%20the%20clappers%20when%20required%20(on%20the%20freeway%2C%20of%20course.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20from%20Box%20Hill%20in%20Surrey%2C%20south%20of%20London%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67dec11169253ccddf9a0d39%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20view%20from%20Box%20Hill%20in%20Surrey%2C%20south%20of%20London.%20Those%20white%20dots%20are%20sheep.%3Cp%3EBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20delivering%20boy-racer%20levels%20of%20acceleration%2C%20that's%20about%20the%20only%20relation%20to%20the%20MGs%20of%20yesteryear%20and%20this%20%26quot%3Bhot%20hatch%26quot%3B%20is%20hard%20to%20get%20too%20excited%20about.%20Given%20that%20it's%20almost%20certain%20to%20never%20go%20on%20sale%20in%20the%20US%2C%20you%20probably%20won't%20have%20to%20grapple%20with%20that%20dilemma.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20was%20in%20the%20market%20for%20an%20EV%20this%20size%2C%20I'm%20not%20convinced%20the%20XPower%20would%20make%20my%20shortlist%20(and%20that%20was%20before%20I%20learned%20the%20MG4%20performed%20very%20poorly%20in%20What%20Car%3F's%20annual%20reliability%20survey.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20what%20I%20think%2C%20the%20MG%20is%20likely%20to%20attract%20some%20buyers%20who%20might%20previously%20have%20considered%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-model-y%