m%2FbA4ontAz1M%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Aman%20Gupta%20(%40amangupta0303)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Famangupta0303%2Fstatus%2F1908778517585625306%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%206%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gupta's%20statement%20comes%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Mr%20Goyal's%20remarks%20at%20the%20event%20Startup%20Mahakumbh.%20The%20minister%20had%20questioned%20whether%20India%20should%20be%20content%20with%20developing%20apps%20that%20deliver%20groceries%20or%20ice%20cream%2C%20especially%20when%20Chinese%20startups%20are%20investing%20in%20semiconductors%2C%20EVs%2C%20and%20AI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20making%20food%2Fhyper%20delivery%20apps%3B%20creating%20cheap%20labour%20so%20the%20rich%20can%20have%20a%20meal%20without%20stepping%20out%2C%20while%20the%20Chinese%20are%20working%20on%20AI%20(artificial%20intelligence)%2C%20EVs%20(electric%20vehicles)%2C%20and%20semiconductors.%20Should%20we%20make%20ice%20cream%20(delivery%20apps)%20or%20make%20chips%20(i.e.%2C%20semiconductors)%3F%20Dukaandari%20hi%20karna%20hai%20(Do%20we%20just%20want%20to%20sell%20things)%3F%20Mr%20Goyal%20asked%20at%20the%20event.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20several%20prominent%20entrepreneurs%20responded%20with%20defensive%20or%20critical%20takes%20on%20Mr%20Goyal's%20comments%2C%20the%20boAT%20chief%20interpreted%20the%20minister's%20address%20as%20a%20motivational%20call%20for%20ambition.%20Drawing%20a%20parallel%20from%20his%20own%20experience%20on%20the%20reality%20show%20Shark%20Tank%20India%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20to%20build%20a%20world-class%20product%2C%20you%20must%20know%20your%20competition.%20That%20applies%20to%20India%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20statement%20stood%20in%20sharp%20contrast%20to%20reactions%20from%20others%20in%20the%20startup%20community%20who%20took%20issue%20with%20Mr%20Goyal's%20remarks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20comments%20drew%20fire%20from%20Zepto%20co-founder%20Aadit%20Palicha%2C%20who%20launched%20into%20a%20detailed%20defence%20of%20consumer%20internet%20startups%20like%20his%20own.%20In%20a%20LinkedIn%20post%2C%20Mr%20Palicha%20cited%20job%20creation%2C%20tax%20contributions%2C%20and%20foreign%20investment%20as%20proof%20of%20real%20economic%20value.%20%26quot%3BAlmost%201.5%20lakh%20real%20people%20are%20earning%20livelihoods%20on%20Zepto%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20that%20isn't%20a%20miracle%20in%20Indian%20innovation%2C%20I%20honestly%20don't%20know%20what%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Palicha%20also%20argued%20that%20many%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20technology%20companies%20-%20Amazon%2C%20Facebook%2C%20Tencent%20-%20began%20as%20consumer%20internet%20platforms%20before%20evolving%20into%20deeper%20tech%20ventures.%20%26quot%3BMost%20technology-led%20innovation%20over%20the%20past%20two%20decades%20has%20originated%20from%20consumer%20internet%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20build%20great%20local%20champions...%20not%20pull%20down%20teams%20that%20are%20trying%20hard%20to%20get%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Infosys%20CFO%20Mohandas%20Pai%20urged%20the%20government%20to%20support%20startups%20rather%20than%20cast%20doubt.%20%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20startups%20in%20all%20those%20areas%20%5Bdeep%20tech%5D%20too%2C%20but%20they%20are%20small.%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20should%20not%20belittle%20our%20startups%20but%20ask%20himself%20what%20he%20has%20done%20to%20help%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20startup%20ecosystem%20had%20been%20historically%20hampered%20by%20policy%20hurdles%20like%20the%20Angel%20Tax%20and%20regulatory%20constraints%20from%20institutions%20like%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOthers%2C%20like%20Shaadi.com%20founder%20Anupam%20Mittal%2C%20acknowledged%20the%20potential%20of%20Indian%20startups%20but%20pointed%20to%20the%20need%20for%20greater%20support.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20few%20months%2C%20I've%20met%20a%20few%20deep-tech%20companies%20that%20have%20absolutely%20blown%20me%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20capital%20and%20the%20ecosystem%20for%20growth%20and%20commercialisation%20are%20severely%20lacking.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20more%20pointed%20response%2C%20former%20BharatPe%20managing%20director%20Ashneer%20Grover%20noted%20that%20even%20China%20began%20with%20consumer%20services%20before%20building%20out%20its%20deep-tech%20industry.%20%26quot%3BChina%20also%20had%20food%20delivery%20first%20and%20then%20evolved%20to%20deep%20tech.%20It's%20great%20to%20aspire%20to%20what%20they've%20done-but%20maybe%20time%20for%20politicians%20to%20aspire%20for%2010%25%2B%20economic%20growth%20for%2020%20years%20flat%20before%20chiding%20today's%20job%20creators%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20posted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20pushback%2C%20Mr%20Goyal%20defended%20his%20remarks%2C%20arguing%20that%20they%20had%20been%20misinterpreted-particularly%20by%20the%20Opposition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20message%20for%20startups%20has%20been%20received%20positively%20except%20by%20some%20Congress%20party%20social%20media%20handles%20who%20are%20hell-bent%20on%20manufacturing%20a%20controversy.%20The%20young%20Indians%20are%20ready%20to%20capture%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20accused%20the%20minister%20of%20contradicting%20the%20government's%20pro-startup%20narrative%2C%20claiming%20on%20social%20media%20that%20Mr%20Goyal%20had%20%26quot%3Badmitted%20India's%20startup%20struggles%26quot%3B%20and%20exposed%20%26quot%3Bthe%20lies%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20startups.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743929040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2F9js1upp8_aman-gupta-piyush-goyal-_625x300_06_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-piyush-goyals-startups-jab-stirs-debate-support-from-boat-founder-aman-gupta-8099919%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aman%20Gupta%2C%20co-founder%20of%20boAT%2C%20has%20stepped%20into%20the%20debate%20over%20India's%20startups%20with%20a%20message%20of%20solidarity%20for%20Union%20Commerce%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%2C%20whose%20recent%20remarks%20drew%20both%20criticism%20and%20concern%20from%20across%20the%20startup%20ecosystem.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20PM%20To%20Admit%20%26quot%3BGlobalisation%20Has%20Failed%26quot%3B%20Amid%20Trump's%20Tariff%20War%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20Kingdom's%20Prime%20Minister%20Keir%20Starmer%20is%20scheduled%20to%20declare%20the%20end%20of%20the%20era%20of%20globalisation%20following%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20hardline%20reciprocal%20tariffs%20and%20'America%20First'%20policy%20that%20triggered%20a%20global%20trade%20war%20pushing%20markets%20into%20the%20shadows%20of%20uncertainty%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20address%20to%20the%20nation%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20British%20Premier%20is%20also%20likely%20to%20admit%20that%20globalization%2C%20which%20started%20after%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20in%201991%2C%20has%20%26quot%3Bfailed%26quot%3B%20millions%20of%20voters%20and%20acknowledge%20why%20Trump's%20economic%20nationalism%20is%20popular%20among%20his%20supporters%20who%20believe%20they%20have%20seen%20no%20benefits%20from%20free%20trade%20and%20mass%20immigration%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22No%20Follow%2C%20No%20Index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.com%2Fuk%2Fpolitics%2Farticle%2Fkeir-starmer-to-admit-globalisation-has-failed-as-tariff-war-rages-s00b6wbcj%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20a%20senior%20UK%20official%2C%20the%20publication%20reported%20that%20while%20the%20UK%20does%20not%20agree%20with%20Trump's%2010%20per%20cent%20%26quot%3Bbaseline%26quot%3B%20tariffs%20and%20other%20recent%20protectionist%20measures%2C%20the%20Starmer%20government%2C%20however%2C%20admits%20that%20a%20new%20era%20has%20begun%20in%20which%20Trump's%20methods%20have%20massive%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BTrump%20has%20done%20something%20that%20we%20don't%20agree%20with%2C%20but%20there's%20a%20reason%20why%20people%20are%20behind%20him%20on%20this.%20The%20world%20has%20changed%2C%20globalisation%20is%20over%2C%20and%20we%20are%20now%20in%20a%20new%20era.%20We've%20got%20to%20demonstrate%20that%20our%20approach%2C%20a%20more%20active%20Labour%20government%2C%20a%20more%20reformist%20government%2C%20can%20provide%20the%20answers%20for%20people%20in%20every%20part%20of%20this%20country%2C'%20the%20report%20cited%20the%20official%20as%20saying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonday's%20address%20will%20be%20Starmer's%20first%20significant%20intervention%20since%20Trump%20imposed%20sweeping%20charges%20on%20imports%2C%20during%20which%20he%20will%20acknowledge%20that%20the%20seismic%20global%20economic%20effects%20prove%20that%20the%20UK%20must%20%26quot%3Bmove%20further%20and%20faster%26quot%3B%20to%20boost%20growth%20with%20supply-side%20reforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20this%20week%2C%20the%20British%20government%20is%20also%20planning%20to%20make%20pro-growth%20announcements%2C%20including%20easing%20regulations%20on%20electric%20car%20manufacturers%20and%20bringing%20forward%20parts%20of%20the%20government's%20industrial%20strategy.%20The%20UK%20is%20due%20to%20hold%20an%20%26quot%3Beconomic%20and%20financial%20dialogue%26quot%3B%20with%20India%20on%20Wednesday%20to%20try%20to%20hasten%20a%20trade%20deal%2C%20while%20efforts%20are%20being%20made%20to%20secure%20a%20new%20agreement%20with%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump's%20Tariffs%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Trump's%20big%20raise%20in%20tariffs%20has%20triggered%20an%20escalating%20trade%20war%20and%20sent%20global%20markets%20plummeting.%20The%20American%20commander-in-chief%20maintained%20that%20his%20new%20levies%20would%20bring%20trillions%20of%20dollars%20of%20investment%20to%20the%20US%20while%20also%20criticizing%20other%20countries'%20retaliatory%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20baseline%2010%20per%20cent%20levy%20announced%20by%20President%20Trump%20this%20week%20kicked%20in%20at%2012%3A01%20a.m.%20Saturday%20ET%20(0401%20GMT)%2C%20triggering%20customs%20agents'%20collections%20at%20ports%20of%20entry%20across%20the%20US.%20Countries%20targeted%20by%20Trump%20for%20higher%20tariffs%20are%20due%20to%20go%20into%20effect%20on%20Wednesday.%20Those%20include%20assessments%20as%20high%20as%2050%20per%20cent%20for%20Lesotho%2C%2049%20per%20cent%20for%20Cambodia%20and%2047%20per%20cent%20for%20Madagascar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20all-caps%20social%20media%20post%20Saturday%2C%20Trump%20insisted%3A%20%26quot%3BTHIS%20IS%20AN%20ECONOMIC%20REVOLUTION%2C%20AND%20WE%20WILL%20WIN.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Trump's%20announcement%2C%20British%20PM%20Starmer%20and%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20agreed%20on%20Saturday%20that%20a%20trade%20war%20was%20in%20no%20one's%20interest%20as%20they%20discussed%20the%20global%20economic%20and%20security%20impact%20of%20the%20tariffs%2C%20particularly%20in%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20Starmer's%20office%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20agreed%20that%20a%20trade%20war%20was%20in%20nobody's%20interests%2C%20but%20nothing%20should%20be%20off%20the%20table%20and%20that%20it%20was%20important%20to%20keep%20business%20updated%20on%20developments%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leaders%20also%20discussed%20efforts%20to%20build%20a%20coalition%20of%20countries%20willing%