ific%20duty%20will%20go%20live%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20worst%20impact%20will%20be%20felt%20by%20the%20electronics%2C%20gems%2C%20and%20jewellery%20sectors%2C%20experts%20fear.%20But%20that%20impact%20will%20be%20limited%20and%20short-term%20because%20of%20the%20country's%20moderate%20share%20in%20global%20exports.%20The%20impact%20of%20the%20tariffs%20on%20competing%20economies%20is%20another%20aspect%20that%20may%20end%20up%20benefiting%20India%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdvantage%20India%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20imposed%20higher%20tariffs%20against%20countries%20like%20China%2C%20Vietnam%20and%20Indonesia%20-%20which%20compete%20with%20India%20in%20the%20export%20sector%20-%20and%20Indian%20exporters%20will%20benefit%20from%20this%2C%20said%20sources.%20India%20has%20the%20first%20mover%20advantage%20since%20it%20is%20the%20only%20country%20that%20began%20negotiations%20with%20the%20US%20for%20a%20Bilateral%20Trade%20Agreement%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%2C%20a%20major%20manufacturing%20hub%20that%20caters%20to%20the%20world%2C%20has%20retaliated%20to%20the%20Trump%20tariffs%20by%20imposing%2034%20per%20cent%20duty%20on%20the%20US.%20But%20India%20did%20not%20make%20any%20such%20move.%20This%20was%20a%20wise%20play%20that%20gives%20India%20an%20edge%20in%20trade%20talks%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20US%20sent%20its%20officials%20only%20to%20India%20for%20negotiations%20on%20tariffs%20after%20Trump%20took%20office%20in%20January.%20India%20and%20US%20are%20now%20trying%20to%20expedite%20the%20bilateral%20trade%20agreement%20that%20will%20be%20mutually%20beneficial%20and%20will%20cover%20a%20range%20of%20issues%20including%20deepening%20supply%20chain%20integration%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Commerce%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20negotiating%20with%20seven%20countries%20for%20a%20free%20trade%20agreement%20and%20trade%20talks%20will%20soon%20begin%20with%20Bahrain%20and%20Qatar%2C%20sources%20pointed%20out%2C%20suggesting%20that%20such%20deals%20would%20resolve%20the%20tariff%20tangle.%20New%20Delhi%20will%20also%20find%20new%20markets%20for%20its%20marine%20and%20jewellery%20products%20and%20other%20sectors%20impacted%20by%20the%20tariffs%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShould%20Exporters%20Fear%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20share%20in%20global%20exports%20has%20doubled%20between%202005%20and%202023.%20It%20stood%20at%202.4%20per%20cent%20in%202023%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20National%20Stock%20Exchange%20(NSE).%20The%20share%20of%20merchandise%20exports%20was%201.8%20per%20cent%20and%20that%20of%20services%20export%20was%204.3%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20US%20is%20the%20world's%20biggest%20economy%20and%20their%20global%20multi-sector%20tariffs%20will%20have%20an%20immediate%20impact%20on%20our%20exporters%2C%20but%20India%20does%20not%20have%20a%20big%20share%20in%20global%20exports%2C%20so%20this%20won't%20impact%20us%20a%20lot%20in%20the%20long%20term%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20PHD%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%20(PHDCCI)%20CEO%20Ranjeet%20Mehta%20while%20talking%20to%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20industry%20body%20assesses%20the%20tariffs%20on%20Indian%20exports%20could%20impact%20only%200.1%25%20of%20the%20GDP%20due%20to%20the%20country's%20price%20competitiveness%20and%20supportive%20government%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStrong%20domestic%20manufacturing%2C%20continued%20government%20handholding%20by%20(introducing)%20strategic%20policy%20measures%20like%20the%20PLI%2C%20Make%20in%20India%2C%20and%20Atmanirbhar%20Bharat%2C%20among%20others%2C%20will%20support%20India's%20growth%20resilience%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hemant%20Jain%2C%20president%2C%20PHDCCI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'New%20Business%20Models%20Will%20Emerge'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20tariffs%20will%20provide%20Indian%20exporters%20an%20opportunity%20to%20expand%20their%20footprint%2C%20said%20Mr%20Mehta%2C%20pointing%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Eapada%20me%20avsar%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20call%20to%20find%20opportunities%20amid%20challenges%20during%20the%20Covid%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNew%20business%20models%20and%20policies%20will%20emerge%20from%20this%20global%20tariff%20war.%20Even%20during%20a%20global%20disaster%20like%20the%20pandemic%2C%20India%20managed%20to%20find%20opportunities%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Mehta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiversification%20and%20innovation%20will%20be%20key%20that%20will%20sustain%20Indian%20exporters%20despite%20the%20challenges.%20Mr%20Mehta%20suggests%20that%20India%20must%20look%20for%20new%20opportunities%20and%20adapt%20to%20the%20changing%20scenario.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20a%20very%20big%20market%20of%201.4%20billion%20people.%20Our%20consumption%20is%20huge.%20India%20is%20still%20the%20fastest-growing%20economy%20in%20emerging%20markets.%20But%20we%20must%20look%20at%20new%20opportunities%20and%20create%20new%20models.%20We%20must%20create%20a%20new%20ecosystem%20that%20will%20help%20us%20make%20our%20products%20more%20innovative%20and%20useful%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpportunities%20Worth%20%2450%20Billion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Federation%20of%20Indian%20Export%20Organizations%20(FIEO)%20expects%20market%20opportunities%20to%20grow%20by%20over%20%2450%20billion%20for%20Indian%20sellers%20due%20to%20the%20tariffs.%20%26quot%3BWe%20assess%20that%20in%20the%20next%20two%20to%20three%20years%2C%20Indian%20exporters%20will%20have%20a%20market%20opportunity%20of%20more%20than%20%24%2050%20billion%20in%20the%20international%20market%20due%20to%20the%20reciprocal%20tariff%20imposed%20by%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20FIEO%20CEO%20Ajay%20Sahai%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjay%20Srivastava%2C%20founder%20of%20think-tank%20Global%20Trade%20Research%20Initiative%20(GTRI)%2C%20too%20said%20the%20tariffs%20present%20a%20strategic%20opportunity%20for%20New%20Delhi%20to%20boost%20its%20presence%20in%20global%20trade%20and%20manufacturing.%20The%20textile%20industry%20may%20benefit%20from%20this.%20Higher%20tariffs%20on%20countries%20like%20China%20and%20Bangladesh%20may%20allow%20Indian%20garment%20manufacturers%20to%20gain%20market%20share%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHigher%20tariffs%20may%20put%20Vietnam%20and%20Thailand%20on%20the%20back%20foot%20and%20India%20-%20with%20initiatives%20like%20the%20Production-Linked%20Incentive%20(PLI)%20scheme%20-%20may%20help%20the%20domestic%20electronics%20manufacturers%20better%20position%20themselves%20in%20the%20global%20markets%2C%20he%20said.%20Similarly%2C%20with%20Taiwan%20facing%20higher%20tariffs%20from%20US%2C%20India%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20emerge%20as%20a%20preferred%20destination%20for%20semiconductor%20manufacturing.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743927240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fl5qravvc_donald-trump-afp_625x300_04_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-tariffs-donald-trump-trump-tariffs-the-surprise-upside-for-india-8098423%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20Indian%20equity%20markets%20panic%20turn%20and%20exporters%20brace%20for%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20tariffs%20to%20kick%20in%2C%20the%20question%20is%20-%20will%20it%20be%20as%20harsh%20as%20feared%3F%20Regardless%20of%20gloom%20forecasters%2C%20pragmatism%20is%20the%20key.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20asked%20200%20retirees%20for%20their%20best%20advice.%20The%20biggest%20tip%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20money.%22%2C%22content%22%