cts%20worth%20over%20Rs%208%2C300%20crore%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPM%20Modi%20witnesses%20Ram%20Setu%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20way%20back%20from%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20PM%20Modi%20witnessed%20the%20Ram%20Setu%20and%20shared%20an%20aerial%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20way%20back%20from%20Sri%20Lanka%20a%20short%20while%20ago%2C%20was%20blessed%20to%20have%20a%20Darshan%20of%20the%20Ram%20Setu.%20And%2C%20as%20a%20divine%20coincidence%2C%20it%20happened%20at%20the%20same%20time%20as%20the%20Surya%20Tilak%20was%20taking%20place%20in%20Ayodhya.%20Blessed%20to%20have%20the%20Darshan%20of%20both.%20Prabhu%20Shri%20Ram%20is%20a%20uniting%20force%20for%20all%20of%20us.%20May%20His%20blessings%20always%20remain%20upon%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOn%20the%20way%20back%20from%20Sri%20Lanka%20a%20short%20while%20ago%2C%20was%20blessed%20to%20have%20a%20Darshan%20of%20the%20Ram%20Setu.%20And%2C%20as%20a%20divine%20coincidence%2C%20it%20happened%20at%20the%20same%20time%20as%20the%20Surya%20Tilak%20was%20taking%20place%20in%20Ayodhya.%20Blessed%20to%20have%20the%20Darshan%20of%20both.%20Prabhu%20Shri%20Ram%20is%20a%20uniting%20force%20for%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FW9lK1UgpmA%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FW9lK1UgpmA%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Narendra%20Modi%20(%40narendramodi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1908780648707612783%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%206%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ERam%20Setu%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20Adams%20Bridge%2C%20is%20a%20chain%20of%20shoals%20linking%20India%20and%20Sri%20Lanka.%20It%20stretches%2048%20km%20between%20Rameswaram%20Island%2C%20off%20the%20southeast%20coast%20of%20Indi