with%20users%20across%20platforms%20sharing%20clips%20of%20the%20yellow%20Pokemon%20weaving%20through%20crowds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EGIANT%20PIKACHU%20spotted%20at%20anti-Trump%20protest%20in%20Washington%20DC.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FiUcyiQpLTF%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FiUcyiQpLTF%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Ford%20Fischer%20(%40FordFischer)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFordFischer%2Fstatus%2F1908571130946048433%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%205%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaturday%20marked%20the%20largest%20day%20of%20demonstrations%20yet%20since%20Trump%20returned%20to%20office%2C%20with%20more%20than%201%2C200%20coordinated%20%26quot%3BHands%20Off!%26quot%3B%20rallies%20sweeping%20across%20all%2050%20states.%20From%20Anchorage%20to%20Miami%2C%20from%20the%20shadow%20of%20the%20Space%20Needle%20in%20Seattle%20to%20Pershing%20Square%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20demonstrators%20flooded%20streets%20to%20oppose%20what%20they%20see%20as%20an%20administration%20determined%20to%20dismantle%20the%20American%20government%20as%20they%20know%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESigns%20reading%20%26quot%3BHands%20off%20our%20democracy%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BHands%20off%20our%20Social%20Security%26quot%3B%20were%20raised%20high%20across%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20turned%20out%20in%20Midtown%20Manhattan.%20In%20Portland%2C%20chants%20rang%20through%20downtown.%20And%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20speakers%20rallied%20the%20crowd%20at%20the%20National%20Mall%20-%20including%20activist%20Graylan%20Hagler%2C%20who%20declared%2C%20%26quot%3BThey've%20woken%20up%20a%20sleeping%20giant%2C%20and%20they%20haven't%20seen%20nothing%20yet%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20per%20an%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtesters%20called%20out%20sweeping%20layoffs%20of%20federal%20wo