aced%20her%20father's%20portrait%20outside.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20Ms%20Tang%20didn't%20realise%20the%20urn%20was%20missing%20and%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20the%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202024%2C%20just%20before%20Valentine's%20Day%2C%20Mr%20Lv%20sent%20Ms%20Tang%20a%20threatening%20letter.%20It%20included%20photos%20of%20the%20stolen%20urn%20and%20a%20message%20saying%20she%20would%20%26quot%3Bnever%20see%20her%20father%20again%26quot%3B%20if%20she%20didn't%20return%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Tang%20reported%20the%20matter%20to%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20coordinated%20with%20the%20military%20to%20inspect%20the%20cemetery%20and%20found%20that%20the%20compartment%20holding%20the%20urn%20had%20been%20broken%20into%2C%20with%20both%20the%20urn%20and%20the%20plaque%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Lv%20was%20already%20in%20prison%20for%20unrelated%20charges%20of%20fraud%20and%20money%20laundering.%20During%20questioning%2C%20he%20denied%20stealing%20the%20urn%2C%20but%20surveillance%20footage%20led%20investigators%20to%20believe%20it%20was%20hidden%20near%20his%20chicken%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2028%2C%20police%20recovered%20the%20urn%20and%20returned%20it%20to%20Ms%20Tang.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELv%20now%20faces%20additional%20charges%20for%20stealing%20and%20damaging%20funerary%20items%2C%20as%20well%20as%20criminal%20intimidation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743923100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fa4mgb6ac_ashes_625x300_06_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftaiwan-man-steals-ex-girlfriends-fathers-ashes-forces-to-get-back-together-8098571%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%2015%20years%20together%2C%20the%20woman%20broke%20off%20the%20relationship%20in%202023%2C%20seeing%20no%20future%20due%20to%20Mr%20Lv's%20growing%20financial%20troubles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F