%20The%20soaring%20unit%2C%20named%20Penthouse%2080%2C%20occupies%20the%20pinnacle%20of%20111%20West%2057th%20Street%2C%20a%201%2C428-foot-tall%20landmark%20on%20Billionaires'%20Row.%20With%20a%20height-to-width%20ratio%20of%2024%3A1%2C%20Steinway%20Tower%20is%20officially%20the%20skinniest%20skyscraper%20in%20the%20world%20-%20far%20outpacing%20the%20Empire%20State%20Building's%201%3A3%20ratio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDesigned%20by%20Studio%20Sofield%2C%20the%20suggested%20layout%20of%20the%20condo%20includes%20five%20bedrooms%2C%20six%20full%20bathrooms%2C%20and%20618%20square%20feet%20of%20exterior%20terraces.%20Each%20of%20the%20building's%20residences%20occupies%20at%20least%20a%20full%20floor%2C%20but%20Penthouse%2080%20takes%20up%20four%20entire%20levels%20-%20a%20rarity%20in%20Manhattan%20real%20estate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20floor%2C%20situated%20on%20the%2080th%20story%2C%20features%20a%20grand%20entry%20hall%20and%20a%20south-facing%20kitchen%20with%20direct%20access%20to%20a%20private%20terrace.%20The%20second%20level%20houses%20four%20bedrooms%20-%20each%20with%20ensuite%20baths%20-%20along%20with%20a%20lounge%20and%20a%20wet%20bar.%20The%20third%20floor%20is%20entirely%20devoted%20to%20a%20massive%202%2C800-square-foot%20primary%20suite%20with%20dual%20bathrooms%20clad%20in%20gray%20and%20white%20onyx.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20the%20top%20floor%2C%20nicknamed%20the%20%26quot%3Bcrown%20suite%2C%26quot%3B%20is%20designed%20for%20entertaining%2C%20having%20a%20bar%2C%20a%20private%20screening%20room%2C%20a%20service%20kitchen%20and%20another%20outdoor%20terrace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20condo%20is%20currently%20vacant%2C%20the%20%24110%20million%20asking%20price%20includes%20a%20full%20buildout%2C%20should%20the%20buyer%20choose%20to%20go%20for%20a%20personalised%20redesign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20very%20healthy%20luxury%20spring%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20lead%20broker%20Nikki%20Field%20of%20Sotheby's%20International%20Realty%20told%20Bloomberg.%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20no%20excuses%20to%20delay%20the%20launch.%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Field%20added%20that%20the%20listing%20was%20strategically%20held%20back%20until%20market%20conditions%20were%20strong%20enough%20to%20support%20its%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20building%20itself%20has%20undergone%20a%20transformation%20in%20recent%20months.%20Since%20taking%20over%20sales%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202024%2C%20Ms%20Field%20and%20her%20team%20at%20Sotheby's%20have%20rebranded%2C%20repriced%20and%20restaffed%20the%20tower%20-%20a%20move%20that%20appears%20to%20be%20paying%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20brokerage%20claims%20%24187%20million%20in%20deals%20are%20currently%20under%20contract%2C%20with%20eight%20units%20already%20in%20play%20this%20year%2C%20including%20Penthouse%2072%2C%20last%20listed%20at%20%2456%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Field%2C%20who%20also%20famously%20handled%20Jeff%20Bezos's%20penthouse%20purchase%20at%20212%20Fifth%20Avenue%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2025%2F04%2F03%2Freal-estate%2Fthis-is-nycs-priciest-home-for-sale%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20NY%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20looking%20for%20Jeff%20Bezos%202.0%20at%20111.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPenthouse%2080%20was%20originally%20two%20duplex%20units%2C%20but%20was%20combined%20into%20one%20grand%20quadplex%20to%20meet%20the%20growing%20appetite%20of%20ultra-high-net-worth%20buyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20all%20been%20to%20very%20luxurious%20places%2C%20but%20I%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20building%20that%20could%20not%20be%20anywhere%20else%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Studio%20Sofield%20founder%20William%20Sofield%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2025%2F04%2F04%2Fstyle%2Fsteinway-tower-penthouse-110-million%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%