l%20visas%20for%20South%20Sudanese%20passport%20holders%20and%20blocking%20new%20arrivals%2C%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%20said%20Saturday%2C%20complaining%20the%20African%20nation%20is%20not%20accepting%20its%20nationals%20expelled%20from%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20State%20Department%20%26quot%3Bis%20taking%20actions%20to%20revoke%20all%20visas%20held%20by%20South%20Sudanese%20passport%20holders%20and%20prevent%20further%20issuance%20to%20prevent%20entry%2C%26quot%3B%20Rubio%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20first%20such%20measure%20singling%20out%20all%20passport%20holders%20from%20a%20particular%20country%20since%20Donald%20Trump%20returned%20to%20the%20White%20House%20on%20January%2020%2C%20having%20campaigned%20on%20an%20anti-immigration%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERubio%20accused%20the%20transitional%20government%20in%20Juba%20of%20%26quot%3Btaking%20advantage%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%26quot%3B%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3Bevery%20country%20must%20accept%20the%20return%20of%20its%20citizens%20in%20a%20timely%20manner%20when%20another%20country...%20seeks%20to%20remove%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWashington%20%26quot%3Bwill%20be%20prepared%20to%20review%20these%20actions%20when%20South%20Sudan%20is%20in%20full%20cooperation%2C%26quot%3B%20Rubio%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20world's%20newest%20country%20and%20also%20one%20of%20the%20poorest%2C%20South%20Sudan%20is%20currently%20prey%20to%20tensions%20between%20political%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20observers%20fear%20a%20renewal%20of%20the%20civil%20war%20that%20killed%20400%2C000%20people%20between%202013%20and%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Sudanese%20nationals%20had%20been%20granted%20%26quot%3Btemporary%20protected%20status%26quot%3B%20(TPS)%20by%20the%20administration%20of%20Trump's%20predecessor%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20with%20the%20designation%20set%20to%20expire%20on%20May%203%2C%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C