20from%20surrounding%20cities%20like%20Santa%20Monica%20and%20Hidden%20Hills%2C%20where%20Kim%20Kardashian%20(%241%20billion)%20resides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E8.%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3ESan%20Francisco%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESan%20Francisco%20is%20home%20to%2058%20billionaires%2C%20with%20a%20combined%20wealth%20of%20%24217%20billion%2C%20averaging%20%243.7%20billion%20per%20individual.%20The%20city%20has%20gained%20eight%20new%20billionaires%20since%20last%20year%2C%20including%20seven%20cofounders%20of%20AI%20company%20Anthropic%2C%20such%20as%20Dario%20and%20Daniela%20Amodei%2C%20each%20worth%20%241.2%20billion.%20Other%20newcomers%20include%20Alexandr%20Wang%20(%242%20billion)%20and%20Vasily%20Shikin%20(%241.7%20billion).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E8.%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3EShanghai%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShanghai%C2%A0dropped%20one%20spot%20to%20tie%20for%20eighth%20place%20with%2058%20billionaires%2C%20despite%20a%20net%20gain%20from%20last%20year's%2054.%20Colin%20Huang%2C%20cofounder%20of%20PDD%20Holdings%2C%20remains%20the%20city's%20richest%20resident%20with%20a%20%2442.3%20billion%20fortune.%20Five%20newcomers%20include%20Du%20Jinhao%20(%241.9%20billion)%20and%20Zhu%20Weisong%20(%241.7%20billion).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%C2%A0Singapore%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingapore%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Ejumped%20two%20spots%20to%20rank%20seventh%2C%20hosting%2060%20billionaires%20with%20a%20combined%20wealth%20of%20%24259%20billion%2C%20a%20significant%20increase%20from%20last%20year.%20Zhang%20Yiming%2C%20cofounder%20of%20ByteDance%20(TikTok's%20parent%20company)%2C%20dominates%20the%20list%20with%20a%20%2465.5%20billion%20fortune%2C%20making%20him%20China's%20richest%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Mumbai%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Edropped%20to%20sixth%20place%2C%20losing%20two%20billionaires%20and%20being%20overtaken%20by%20London%20and%20Beijing.%20Mukesh%20Ambani%2C