c%20design%20opportunities%20in%20Udaipur%20meant%20she%20had%20to%20carve%20a%20new%20path.%20She%20began%20organising%20artist%20camps%2C%20helping%20potters%20and%20artisans%20create%20new%20products%2C%20and%20soon%20started%20working%20with%20the%20NGO%20Seva%20Mandir%2C%20designing%20visual%20communication%20tools%20for%20rural%20communities.%20%E2%80%9CI%20could%20have%20moved%20back%20to%20Ahmedabad%20and%20pursued%20ceramics%2C%20but%20at%20the%20time%2C%20having%20a%20long-distance%20marriage%20just%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20considered%20acceptable%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESketching%20periods%20into%20the%20picture%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakshmi%E2%80%99s%20first%20real%20brush%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F246267%2Fmenstrual-hygiene-kit-cloth-pads-avni-safepads-women-health-ana79%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emenstrual%20health%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecame%20while%20developing%20training%20materials%20for%20non-literate%20communities.%20She%20realised%20the%20visuals%20she%20was%20drawing%20didn%E2%80%99t%20resonate%20with%20people.%20%E2%80%9CThose%20who%20haven%E2%80%99t%20been%20to%20school%20have%20a%20completely%20different%20way%20of%20drawing.%20So%2C%20I%20created%20a%20picture%20dictionary%20on%20how%20menstruation%2C%20abortion%2C%20and%20delivery%20should%20be%20depicted.%20That%20became%20the%20basis%20for%20our%20training%20manuals%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.co